SpatialReference Table
    GET /api/spatial-reference
        Retrieve all spatial references.
    GET /api/spatial-reference/:id
        Retrieve a specific spatial reference by its ID (epsg_code).
    POST /api/spatial-reference
        Insert a new spatial reference (RESTRICTED to superusers/admins).
    PUT /api/spatial-reference/:id
        Update a specific spatial reference (RESTRICTED).
    DELETE /api/spatial-reference/:id
        Delete a specific spatial reference (RESTRICTED).
    
